    <item>
      <title>加沙和航运冲突加剧，伊朗陆军推出新硬件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/iran-army-unveils-new-hardware-as-gaza-shipping-conflicts-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗军方周日在国家电视台报道中透露了一系列新装备，重点介绍了射程可达1000公里的新型巡航导弹、具有“电子战和情报”能力的无人机以及用于侦察和攻击的直升机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-24/iran-army-unveils-new-hardware-as-gaza-shipping-conflicts-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 08:19:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙激烈战斗导致 13 名以色列士兵死亡，哈马斯深入推进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-24/a-weekend-of-combat-in-gaza-kills-more-than-a-dozen-israeli-soldiers-a-sign-of-hamas-entrenchment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙代尔巴拉赫（美联社）以色列军方周日表示，周末有 15 名以色列士兵在加沙的战斗中丧生，同时仍在继续尝试达成另一笔与以色列扣押的巴勒斯坦人交换人质的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-24/a-weekend-of-combat-in-gaza-kills-more-than-a-dozen-israeli-soldiers-a-sign-of-hamas-entrenchment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 08:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚寻求控制与前央行行长有关的银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-23/nigeria-to-buy-banks-purchased-by-ousted-central-bank-governor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚正在寻求对两家银行的控制权，总统博拉·蒂努布发起的一项调查称，前中央银行行长戈德温·埃梅菲勒(Godwin Emefiele)利用代理人以大幅折扣收购了这两家银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-23/nigeria-to-buy-banks-purchased-by-ousted-central-bank-governor</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Dec 2023 13:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
